data.description: Welcome to this charming 5 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home nestled on a serene 5-acre lot in the heart of Georgetown. Step inside to discover a beautifully updated kitchen, complete with modern appliances and sleek countertops. The interior boasts a harmonious blend of luxury vinyl plank and plush carpeting, providing both style and comfort. With a versatile unfinished basement, the possibilities for customization are endless. The primary bedroom, situated on the second floor, is a true retreat, featuring a spacious en suite bathroom and a generously sized closet. Three additional bedrooms on the main floor offer flexibility for guests, a home office, or a growing family. The convenience of a full bathroom on the main floor ensures everyone's needs are met. Enjoy your morning coffee or evening relaxation on the expansive wrap-around porch, where you can soak in the peaceful ambiance of your 5-acre oasis. This home offers the perfect combination of space, comfort, and tranquility. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make it your own!
